{"tid":663301,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"PS4 PRO CLUB 招收全職中堅及龍門","createTime":"2018-05-13T07:47:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-15T14:02:19.000Z","uid":34279,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3e3fdb0b231782beedd5827ba003e3185186467a","tid":663301,"uid":34279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T07:47:41.000Z","msg":"D1球隊為提升防守能力，希望招收以下位置：<br />\n<br />\n中堅：擁有良好位置感和判斷力，作為龍門前最後防線，需要和防中配合防守。需有一定頭球防守能力。傳波以安全第一為首要目標。<br />\n<br />\n龍門：需要有一定經驗，不要新手龍門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 懂得彈跳救球。擁有精準龍門球技術更好。<br />\n<br />\n隊伍陣式及打法：4231/433。<br />\n有常駐ANY，主要為中間地面短傳進攻，當然也會長傳，只在適當時機放直線。<br />\n<br />\n全體要求：<br />\n- 尊重隊友，不需要獨食鳩扭個人主義者，需要以球隊利益為先。<br />\n- 多走位幫波，不要只向前衝。希望球員盡量做到護球在腳。<br />\n- 不要瘋狂放直線至死位，適當時懂橫傳及後傳。<br />\n- 禁止瘋狂浪射（即明知射門路線被封卻不傳而射龜者）。<br />\n- 需要多溝通交流討論，幫助大家進步。<br />\n- 只收全職球員。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有能力及有意試腳者請留TG，謝謝。"},{"pid":"164a40e0939dc4d88963114cb61f20da0c781e51","tid":663301,"uid":34279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T10:03:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20972b3e66d01aa2cbfdc8795a33914ba6e12458","tid":663301,"uid":60506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T12:28:51.000Z","msg":"彈跳救球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即係咩 <br />\n飛撲定出迎打高波"},{"pid":"87e28cedcb042e6e8c0da5339e644cc700064bf4","tid":663301,"uid":34279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20972b3e66d01aa2cbfdc8795a33914ba6e12458","tid":663301,"uid":60506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T12:28:51.000Z","msg":"彈跳救球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即係咩 <br />\n飛撲定出迎打高波"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T13:21:23.000Z","msg":"Why not both<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d255968774056a7d0fae1bd91037340cc2ff3ee3","tid":663301,"uid":34279,"like":0,"dislike"